author: Home Repair Tutor
description: I love this @zipwall_llc magnetic dust barrier door kit. I use it with 6 mil plastic and two poles to separate my work area from the rest of the home. You can tape the plastic to the walls or use Foam Rails for an even better seal. It’s definitely a must for containing dusty work areas…many thanks to ZipWall for sponsoring this video and msking products that protect people & pets👍🏽🔥
title: Dust Control Tips - #shorts #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
